tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE team_performance (
    team_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_name VARCHAR(255),
    team_leader VARCHAR(255),
    performance_score FLOAT,
    engagement_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE team_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_name VARCHAR(255),
    team_id INT,
    joining_date DATE,
    performance_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE team_scores (
    score_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_id INT,
    score_date DATE,
    efficiency_score INT,
    engagement_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE team_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    performance_insights TEXT,
    engagement_insights TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE virtual_team_leaders (
    team_leader_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_name VARCHAR(255),
    team_size INT,
    location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE team_performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_leader_id INT,
    date DATE,
    performance_score FLOAT,
    feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE team_engagement (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_leader_id INT,
    date DATE,
    engagement_score FLOAT,
    comments TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE team_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

    member_name VARCHAR(255),

)

CREATE TABLE VirtualTeamLeaders (
    leader_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

)

CREATE TABLE TeamPerformance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

)

CREATE TABLE TeamEngagement (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

)

CREATE TABLE TeamMembers (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

    team_id INT,
    join_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE TeamTasks (
    task_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
